    bibo:volume "3905" ;
    dc:creator "Delgado-Blas, Víctor Hugo" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Prionospio (Polychaeta, Spionidae) from the Grand Caribbean Region, with the descriptions of five new species and a key to species recorded in the area" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287676> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287676>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Prionospio rotunda sp. nov. holotype (LACM-AHF-POLY 6601: A, H – M; paratype LACM-AHF-POLY 6602: B – G, N – O): (A) anterior region, dorsal view; (B) anterior region, lateral view; (C) left palp; (D) parapodium of anterior chaetigers (1 – 5); (E) parapodium of chaetigers 7 – 8; (F) parapodium of chaetiger 14; (G) parapodium of chaetiger 40; (H) notopodium of chetigers 5 – 7 and high dorsal crest; (I) anterior notopodial chaeta; (J) anterior neuropodial chaeta; (K) sabre chaeta; (L) neuropodial hooded hook; (M) notopodial hooded hook; (N) pygidium, dorsal view; (O) parasite shown within the host´s body cavity between chaetigers 25 – 27. Scale bars: A – M 50 µm; N – O 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287676/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

